"Obligation (ECO4) may be available. If the service gives an indication that "
"the user and their property may be eligible for support, based on "
"information that the user is invited to provide, then they can create a "
"referral that will make their details available to an energy supplier. This "
"will usually be their own energy provider unless the user themselves selects "
"another."
msgstr ""
"Mae gwasanaeth Gwirio’ch Cymhwystra ar gyfer Cynllun Inswleiddio Mawr "
