"chraffu ar y gwasanaeth y byddwn yn cadw'ch data personol."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:132
msgid ""
"Personal data will be retained for up to two years after the GB Insulation "
"Scheme has ended. Following this, the data will be securely deleted after "
"collection in line with the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero "
"policy."
