"Yn ystod y cyfnod hwn bydd modd iddo gael ei weld gan yr Adran Diogelwch "
"Ynni a Sero Net a'ch cyflenwr ynni."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:139
msgid "Your rights"
msgstr "Eich hawliau"

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:142
msgid ""
"You have the right to request information about how your personal data are "
"processed, and to request a copy of that personal data."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i ofyn am wybodaeth am sut mae'ch data personol yn cael "
"ei brosesu, ac i ofyn am gopi o'r data personol hwnnw."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:145
msgid ""
"You have the right to request that any inaccuracies in your personal data "
"are rectified without delay. You have the right to request that any "
"incomplete personal data are completed, including by means of a "
"supplementary statement."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i ofyn i unrhyw anghywirdebau yn eich data personol "
"gael eu cywiro'n ddi-oed. Mae gennych chi hawl i ofyn i unrhyw ddata "
"personol anghyflawn gael ei gwblhau, gan gynnwys trwy ddatganiad atodol."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:148
msgid ""
"You have the right to request that your personal data are erased if there is "
"no longer a justification for them to be processed."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i ofyn i'ch data personol gael ei ddileu os nad oes "
"cyfiawnhad dros ei brosesu mwyach."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:151
msgid ""
"You have the right in certain circumstances (for example, where accuracy is "
"contested) to request that the processing of your personal data is "
"restricted."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl dan rai amgylchiadau (er enghraifft, pan fyddwch chi'n "
"dadlau nad yw'n gywir) i ofyn i'r gwaith prosesu ar eich data personol gael "
"ei gyfyngu."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:154
msgid ""
"You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data where "
"it is processed for direct marketing purposes."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i wrthwynebu prosesu'ch data personol pan fo'n cael ei "
"brosesu at ddibenion marchnata uniongyrchol."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:157
msgid ""
"You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data "
"including the right to object to automated processing."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i wrthwynebu prosesu'ch data personol gan gynnwys yr "
"hawl i wrthwynebu prosesu awtomataidd."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:161
msgid "International transfers"
msgstr "Trosglwyddiadau rhyngwladol"

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:165
msgid ""
"We design, build and run our systems to make sure that your data is as safe "
"as possible at all stages, both while it's processed and when it's stored."
msgstr ""
"Rydyn ni'n dylunio, yn adeiladu ac yn rhedeg ein systemau i sicrhau bod eich "
"data mor ddiogel â phosibl ym mhob cyfnod, a hynny tra bo'n cael ei brosesu "
"a phan gaiff ei storio."

#: help_to_heat/templates/frontdoor/privacy-policy.html:169
msgid ""
"As your personal data is stored on our IT infrastructure and shared with our "
"data processors Microsoft, GOV.UK Notify and Amazon Web Services, it may be "
"transferred and stored securely in the UK and European Economic Area. Where "
"it is the case that your personal data is stored outside the UK and EEA it "
"will be subject to equivalent legal protection through the use of Model "
"Contract Clauses."
msgstr ""
